{"tid":1325740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳示威者鉗斷警員手指「工具」實為警棍 警方誤放消息低調修改","createTime":"2019-07-17T03:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T03:34:02.000Z","uid":39808,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3b0847a64be1bd0599a69c5a45dc9b216da93a63","tid":1325740,"uid":39808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T03:34:02.000Z","msg":"沙田新城市廣場周日(7月14日)發生嚴重警民衝突，多間媒體引述警方指，有警員被示威者用鉗剪斷手指，傳真社調查發現，被指鉗斷警員手指的工具，實為示威者從警員手上搶去的警棍，該警員手指事後亦完好無缺。<br />\n<br />\n完整報導<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.factwire.org/investigation/%e5%82%b3%e7%a4%ba%e5%a8%81%e8%80%85%e9%89%97%e6%96%b7%e8%ad%a6%e5%93%a1%e6%89%8b%e6%8c%87%e3%80%8c%e5%b7%a5%e5%85%b7%e3%80%8d%e5%af%a6%e7%82%ba%e8%ad%a6%e6%a3%8d-%e8%ad%a6%e6%96%b9%e8%aa%a4%e6%94%be/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.factwire.org%2Finvestigation%2F%25e5%2582%25b3%25e7%25a4%25ba%25e5%25a8%2581%25e8%2580%2585%25e9%2589%2597%25e6%2596%25b7%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e5%2593%25a1%25e6%2589%258b%25e6%258c%2587%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e5%2585%25b7%25e3%2580%258d%25e5%25af%25a6%25e7%2582%25ba%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%25a3%258d-%25e8%25ad%25a6%25e6%2596%25b9%25e8%25aa%25a4%25e6%2594%25be%2F&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=fa9a6678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.factwire.org/investigation/%e5%82%b3%e7%a4%ba%e5%a8%81%e8%80%85%e9%89%97%e6%96%b7%e8%ad%a6%e5%93%a1%e6%89%8b%e6%8c%87%e3%80%8c%e5%b7%a5%e5%85%b7%e3%80%8d%e5%af%a6%e7%82%ba%e8%ad%a6%e6%a3%8d-%e8%ad%a6%e6%96%b9%e8%aa%a4%e6%94%be/</a>"}]}